SUMMARY:[Wk2] Ch 2 тАФ Understanding Foundation Models + Hands-On ML
DESCRIPTION:WEEK 2/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ AI Engineering (Huyen)\nChapter: Ch 2 тАФ Understanding Foundation Models\nFocus: Transformers\, attention\, pre-training vs post-training\, tokenisation\, context windows\, sampling params. Dense chapter.\nтЬЕ Practice: Experiment with temperature + sampling params using LLM API. Tokenise sentences with Hugging Face tokeniser.\n\nЁЯУЪ Hands-On ML (G├йron)\nChapter: Ch 2 тАФ End-to-End ML Project (HEAVIEST)\nFocus: California housing: cleaning\, feature engineering\, pipelines\, cross-validation\, hyperparameter tuning.\nтЬЕ Practice: Do every step manually before copying code. Build your own Pipeline + ColumnTransformer. Most important chapter in Part 1.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 2 тАФ Understanding Foundation Models\n    тЖТ Experiment with temperature + sampling params using LLM API. Tokenise sente\n[ ] Ch 2 тАФ End-to-End ML Project (HEAVIEST)\n    тЖТ Do every step manually before copying code. Build your own Pipeline + Colum\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
