SUMMARY:[Wk5] Ch 5 тАФ Prompt Engineering + Hands-On ML
DESCRIPTION:WEEK 5/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ AI Engineering (Huyen)\nChapter: Ch 5 тАФ Prompt Engineering\nFocus: System prompts\, few-shot examples\, chain-of-thought\, structured outputs (JSON mode)\, prompt chaining.\nтЬЕ Practice: Add 3 prompt variants to eval harness. Run eval across all three. Compare scores. Systematic prompt engineering.\n\nЁЯУЪ Hands-On ML (G├йron)\nChapter: Ch 5-6 тАФ SVMs + Decision Trees + XGBoost\nFocus: SVM: margin\, kernels (linear/RBF/polynomial). Decision Trees: CART\, Gini\, depth. XGBoost intro.\nтЬЕ Practice: Train SVM on non-linear data with RBF kernel. Visualise decision tree with export_graphviz. Compare depths.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 5 тАФ Prompt Engineering\n    тЖТ Add 3 prompt variants to eval harness. Run eval across all three. Compare s\n[ ] Ch 5-6 тАФ SVMs + Decision Trees + XGBoost\n    тЖТ Train SVM on non-linear data with RBF kernel. Visualise decision tree with \n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
