SUMMARY:[Wk8] Ch 8 тАФ Dataset Engineering + Hands-On ML
DESCRIPTION:WEEK 8/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ AI Engineering (Huyen)\nChapter: Ch 8 тАФ Dataset Engineering\nFocus: Data collection\, deduplication\, cleaning\, synthetic data generation\, annotation\, formatting for fine-tuning.\nтЬЕ Practice: Audit your RAG pipeline documents тАФ what's noisy\, duplicated\, missing? Write short data quality report.\n\nЁЯУЪ Hands-On ML (G├йron)\nChapter: Ch 9 тАФ Unsupervised Learning\nFocus: K-Means\, DBSCAN\, Gaussian Mixture Models\, anomaly detection\, density estimation.\nтЬЕ Practice: Apply K-Means to real dataset. Elbow method + silhouette score. DBSCAN on non-convex clusters.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 8 тАФ Dataset Engineering\n    тЖТ Audit your RAG pipeline documents тАФ what's noisy\, duplicated\, missing? Writ\n[ ] Ch 9 тАФ Unsupervised Learning\n    тЖТ Apply K-Means to real dataset. Elbow method + silhouette score. DBSCAN on n\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
