SUMMARY:[Wk9] Ch 9 тАФ Inference Optimisation + Hands-On ML
DESCRIPTION:WEEK 9/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ AI Engineering (Huyen)\nChapter: Ch 9 тАФ Inference Optimisation\nFocus: Quantisation\, KV cache\, batching\, speculative decoding\, distillation\, goodput. Making inference cheap for production.\nтЬЕ Practice: Benchmark RAG pipeline: latency\, tokens/sec\, cost per query. Try smaller model. Record quality-latency-cost trade-off.\n\nЁЯУЪ Hands-On ML (G├йron)\nChapter: Part 1 Review + тШЕ PORTFOLIO PROJECT 1\nFocus: Review Chs 1-9 exercises. Then build first portfolio project.\nтЬЕ Practice: тШЕ PROJECT 1: Full Scikit-Learn pipeline on Kaggle dataset тАФ cleanтЖТfeaturesтЖТcompare(LR/RF/XGB)тЖТtuneтЖТevaluate. GitHub portfolio piece.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 9 тАФ Inference Optimisation\n    тЖТ Benchmark RAG pipeline: latency\, tokens/sec\, cost per query. Try smaller mo\n[ ] Part 1 Review + тШЕ PORTFOLIO PROJECT 1\n    тЖТ тШЕ PROJECT 1: Full Scikit-Learn pipeline on Kaggle dataset тАФ cleanтЖТfeaturesтЖТ\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
