DESCRIPTION:WEEK 23/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ Hands-On ML (G├йron)\nChapter: тШЕ Capstone Week 2 тАФ Model + Training\nFocus: Train your deep learning model. Iterate on architecture + hyperparameters. Track experiments. Beat baseline.\nтЬЕ Practice: тШЕ CAPSTONE WK 2: Run 5+ training runs with different hyperparams. Log with W&B free tier. Pick best checkpoint.\n\nЁЯУЪ DDIA 2nd Ed. (Kleppmann)\nChapter: Ch 10 тАФ Consistency + Consensus Part 1 (тШЕ HARDEST CHAPTER)\nFocus: Linearisability vs eventual consistency. CAP theorem and its misuse. Causality and causal consistency.\nтЬЕ Practice: Read once through. Then write half-page on linearisability vs causal consistency WITHOUT looking at the book.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] тШЕ Capstone Week 2 тАФ Model + Training\n    тЖТ тШЕ CAPSTONE WK 2: Run 5+ training runs with different hyperparams. Log with \n[ ] Ch 10 тАФ Consistency + Consensus Part 1 (тШЕ HARDEST CHAPTER)\n    тЖТ Read once through. Then write half-page on linearisability vs causal consis\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
