DESCRIPTION:WEEK 33/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ Patterns Dist. Systems (Joshi)\nChapter: Ch 21-24 тАФ Two-Phase Commit\, Lamport Clock\, Hybrid Clock\, Clock-Bound Wait\nFocus: Atomic updates across nodes. Logical timestamps without wall-clock. Combine physical + logical. Pause for clock uncertainty.\nтЬЕ Practice: Clock-Bound Wait = Google Spanner TrueTime. Read Spanner paper abstract. How does TrueTime differ from NTP?\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 21-24 тАФ Two-Phase Commit\, Lamport Clock\, Hybrid Clock\, Clock-B\n    тЖТ Clock-Bound Wait = Google Spanner TrueTime. Read Spanner paper abstract. Ho\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
