DESCRIPTION:WEEK 34/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ Patterns Dist. Systems (Joshi)\nChapter: Ch 25-29 тАФ Consistent Core\, Lease\, State Watch\, Gossip Dissemination\, Emergent Leader\nFocus: Small strongly-consistent cluster coordinates larger cluster. Time-bounded locks. Client subscriptions. Epidemic spread. Age-based election.\nтЬЕ Practice: Map ZooKeeper: znodesтЖТConsistent Core\, ephemeral nodesтЖТLease\, watchersтЖТState Watch. Then map same to Kubernetes+etcd.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 25-29 тАФ Consistent Core\, Lease\, State Watch\, Gossip Disseminat\n    тЖТ Map ZooKeeper: znodesтЖТConsistent Core\, ephemeral nodesтЖТLease\, watchersтЖТStat\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
