DESCRIPTION:WEEK 35/36 тАФ AI Engineer Learning Roadmap\n================================================\n\nЁЯУЪ Patterns Dist. Systems (Joshi)\nChapter: Ch 30-32 тАФ Single-Socket Channel\, Request Batch\, Request Pipeline\nFocus: One TCP connection per server pair preserves ordering. Combine requests for throughput. Send multiple without waiting.\nтЬЕ Practice: Map to Kafka producer: linger.msтЖТRequest Batch delay\, batch.sizeтЖТbatch size\, max.in.flightтЖТpipeline depth. Tuning becomes principled.\n\n--- WEEKLY CHECKLIST ---\n[ ] Ch 30-32 тАФ Single-Socket Channel\, Request Batch\, Request Pipeline\n    тЖТ Map to Kafka producer: linger.msтЖТRequest Batch delay\, batch.sizeтЖТbatch size\n\nтП▒я╕П Session 1/5: Deep Read + Theory\nЁЯУЕ 10-12 hrs/week ┬╖ Huyen ┬╖ G├йron ┬╖ DDIA 2nd Ed ┬╖ Joshi
